data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Hope, North Dakota! This charming property on an expansive 17,000+ square foot lot offers endless possibilities. Inside, the home exudes charm and warmth with beautiful hardwood floors. Stay comfortable year-round with the recently installed central air system and electric forced air furnace, ensuring a cozy environment regardless of the season.  Say goodbye to cold mornings in the kitchen with heated floors, making meal preparation a pleasure, even in the chilliest weather.  Contact your favorite Realtor today for a showing. *Agent related to sellers*
